{"tid":1841654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"自從黑心救救口罩被起底  各區出現保鮮袋裝口罩","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:57:41.000Z","uid":262146,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"89c8c348da27e855026d599819ec7365801ee391","tid":1841654,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztcn2fT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fztcn2fT.jpg&h=d8d69fc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf1729aea62e3a56c7efea2cc009aafaf795e24d","tid":1841654,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"Chi lun 7 sin"},{"pid":"3228f9ed994e9410579836c9b16ad9e57ee6718c","tid":1841654,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89c8c348da27e855026d599819ec7365801ee391","tid":1841654,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztcn2fT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fztcn2fT.jpg&h=d8d69fc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1b346ab3f285e6963a6b1e55bf209003a7b131","tid":1841654,"uid":262146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"香港黑心藥房，以前就賺水貨客錢，搞到民不聊生<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中，佢地就做撐警藍絲<br />\n<br />\n而家疫症，仲要賣黑心口罩<br />\n<br />\n到底班藥房佬幾時死"},{"pid":"a5db6bdc76df0d4b72c503df036189d53d344642","tid":1841654,"uid":249766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"點撚解有人咁on9仲會買..."},{"pid":"aa75d6106188ab154d7bba9368ad759a4c9636e9","tid":1841654,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"藥房狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30b54e7ab5f5861d5933ab491586a0afab30d83","tid":1841654,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"6天蓋出「火神山醫院」不夠用！武漢決定旁邊再蓋一所「雷神山」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669737.jpg&h=1816b700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲為了再6天內蓋出「火神山醫院」，大陸調動上百台挖土機整地。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n記者蔡紹堅／綜合報導<br />\n武漢市防疫指揮部23日決定參照SARS期間7天建成的「小湯山醫院」，在6天內興建一所武漢肺炎的專門醫院，定名為「火神山醫院」。不過，似乎是考量到「火神山」的床位有限，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午決定，要在2月5日前在「火神山」旁再建一所「雷神山醫院」。<br />\n「火神山醫院」的承建單位中建三局人員透露，火神山醫院的面積為2.5萬平方公尺，可容納1000張床，規劃在6天內建成，也就是說會在2月1日完工，2月3日投入使用。<br />\n<strong>▼挖土機通宵趕工，為了達成6天蓋出醫院的目標。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669734.jpg&h=9699b0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了達成6天完工的目標，中建三局23日晚上就展開動作，調集上百台挖土機、推土機等施工機械抵達工地，通宵進行場平、回填等施工。主體的施工則從25日開始，整個施工期間，項目部將按照兩班倒的方式日夜不停施工，高峰期將有1500名建設者和280台套施工機械設備同時奮戰。<br />\n不過，似乎是考量到「火神山醫院」的1000個床位不夠用，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午3點半舉行調度會，決定在「火神山醫院」旁邊，在2月5日前再建成一所「雷神山醫院」，新增床位1300張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669716.jpg&h=fa4a9f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，多名醫護也遭感染。（圖／武漢中心醫院）</strong>"},{"pid":"abf046255473e44905ac29931de39ba1e12c0168","tid":1841654,"uid":59518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a1b346ab3f285e6963a6b1e55bf209003a7b131","tid":1841654,"uid":262146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"香港黑心藥房，以前就賺水貨客錢，搞到民不聊生<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中，佢地就做撐警藍絲<br />\n<br />\n而家疫症，仲要賣黑心口罩<br />\n<br />\n到底班藥房佬幾時死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"我條村商場間藥房算有趣<br />\n奶粉永遠mark up 只留比蝗<br />\n但日常用品就賣好平 <br />\n前日賣口罩 60／50個 made in Taiwan 限一人一盒 仲有真日本獨立包裝口罩"},{"pid":"16a7e7bf488b5d89ff22131d878f80f5928fedd2","tid":1841654,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"深水埗d自粘貼散裝口罩全部都係一盒拆出黎人口逐個入，口罩亂咁放，又無戴手套，又摸到中間，極度唔污糟<br />\n<br />\n要買就一盒過買，或者真係封實咗嘅獨立包裝"},{"pid":"a5c05c01ae9217088fb7f9402729302fd11f8469","tid":1841654,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深水埗d自粘貼散裝口罩全部都係一盒拆出黎人<span style=\"color: red;\">手</span>逐個入，口罩亂咁放，又無戴手套，又摸到中間，極度<span style=\"color: red;\">污糟</span><br />\n<br />\n要買就一盒過買，或者真係封實咗嘅獨立包裝</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e87061a9dcab0820c8854d327cf6866b90bb37a3","tid":1841654,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1841600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1841600</a>"},{"pid":"a08affd27df6e23387f7ccfb316290574e5c2ec5","tid":1841654,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"千祈唔撚好買呢d"},{"pid":"cbbb26ffa15b3be0e3d365fcd40cd6b57d090a12","tid":1841654,"uid":271173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"情願研究點樣上Amazon集運買口罩<br />\n都好過去藥房買！<br />\n有 d 藥房就算唔賣 reuse 口罩<br />\n都係呃你賣 d 唔岩 ASTM standard 既俾你"},{"pid":"93083b4a4d236b2f66456ac818bf14ac53895488","tid":1841654,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"藥房仆街死全家過唔到年"},{"pid":"228094ebf3fc0ea9fbce5a217fb680a13e1ca5ce","tid":1841654,"uid":11793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"係街執完用過再PACK返好賣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036af276f70e370427f66dd4ffaccfba582a54d5","tid":1841654,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"入黑名單，過完年就幫你開年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\"